<br><br>
Mr. Bakshi is a triumphant professional in the competitive Indian White Goods landscape. He represents the all-too-rare combination of thinker, doer and leader, and his vast expertise and experience in the Appliances domain makes him a distinct professional. Under his able leadership, Voltas has consistently grown in revenue and profitability, well ahead of the industry. In fact, Voltas achieved leadership position in Market Share, and has also scored highest in terms of Brand Equity, under his stewardship.
<br><br>
An enthusiastic and confident leader, Mr. Pradeep Bakshi has been the Appliances Man of the Year 2013, and has also received the President’s award for Energy Conservation, amongst many other awards and accolades during the last one decade.</p>
