He is a dynamic mentor with exceptional People and HR skills, with specialised knowledge in areas of thought leadership and growth orientation. He combines strong proven business acumen with a sense of purpose.
<br/><br/>
He has also been a speaker at various acclaimed platforms imparting his immense professional knowledge and experiences.</p>
